				<p>Storm damage compromising your security? Fence down creating safety concerns? We offer 24/7 emergency fence repair services for urgent situations throughout Sacramento County.</p>
				<a href="tel:916-555-3362" class="btn emergency-btn">Call for Emergency Service: (916) 555-FENCE</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
